    result = ImmedLockPort(port,passwd,reason,pri,bc)
                           A0   A1     A2     D0  A3
    LONG ImmedLockPort(char *,char *,char *,char,char *)

  FUNCTION
    Locks a port with an "immediate" lock.  This means that the function
    will return immediately, regardless of whether a lock was obtained.
